data.description: 2.25% VA Loan Assumption available. Buyer must have VA eligibility and pay the difference to meet sales price.**Step into the realm of luxurious accessibility with this stunning two-story home, fully ADA certified to cater to exceptional comfort and convenience. With 6 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, the main level encompasses a spacious kitchen, inviting living room, elegant dining area, well-appointed office, convenient half bathroom, utility room, and a primary bedroom featuring a lavish ensuite. The second level unveils an additional family room, 5 bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms, all impeccably maintained. The kitchen is a masterpiece, adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and custom built-ins in the pantry, complemented by a sprawling island and abundant cabinet space. The living room offers lofty ceilings and a captivating stone fireplace. The primary bedroom serves as a retreat, boasting exquisite wood flooring, a shiplap accent wall, and a beautifully crafted barn sliding door leading to the ensuite. The ensuite has been thoughtfully designed with dual sinks, an abundance of cabinet space, a magnificent shiplap accent wall, a grand glass walk-in shower, and a capacious closet complete with custom built-in cabinetry. Each additional bedroom features a ceiling fan, with one upstairs closet transformed into a tailored office space with a custom built-in desk. The laundry room is equipped with a sink and built-in cabinets, while the garage boasts its own set of built-in cabinets, air conditioned/insulated with a mini split unit. The backyard beckons with an expansive extended covered patio featuring a ceiling fan, outdoor kitchen, rejuvenating jacuzzi, and greenbelt. Adding to its allure, the home is equipped with solar panels. This home encompasses all the finest features, offering a symphony of comfort and sophistication-truly an opportunity not to be missed.
